<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Category Overspend Alert - {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #c0392b);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .alert-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .alert-message {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .category-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px solid #e74c3c;
        }
        .category-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .category-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: {{categoryColor}};
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .category-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .budget-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .budget-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .amount {
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .overspend {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            height: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #c0392b);
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .recent-transactions {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .transaction-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .transaction-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .transaction-description {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
        .transaction-date {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .transaction-amount {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-left: 15px;
        }
        .actions {
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .tips {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .tips h3 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .tips ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .budget-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            .button {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
            .transaction-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            .transaction-amount {
                margin-left: 0;
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <span class="alert-icon">ðŸ“Š</span>
            <h1>Category Overspend Alert</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello {{firstName}},</h2>
            
            <div class="alert-message">
                <strong>You've exceeded your category budget!</strong> 
                Your spending in the <strong>{{categoryName}}</strong> category has exceeded its allocated budget.
            </div>
            
            <div class="category-details">
                <div class="category-header">
                    <div class="category-icon" style="background-color: {{categoryColor}};">
                        {{categoryIcon}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="category-name">{{categoryName}}</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div class="progress-fill" style="width: {{#if (gt utilizationPercentage 100)}}100{{else}}{{utilizationPercentage}}{{/if}}%;">
                        {{utilizationPercentage}}%
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="budget-row">
                    <span>Budget Period:</span>
                    <span>{{budgetPeriod}} ({{startDate}} - {{endDate}})</span>
                </div>
                <div class="budget-row">
                    <span>Category Budget:</span>
                    <span class="amount">{{currency}}{{categoryBudget}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="budget-row">
                    <span>Amount Spent:</span>
                    <span class="amount">{{currency}}{{categorySpent}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="budget-row">
                    <span>Over Budget By:</span>
                    <span class="amount overspend">{{currency}}{{overAmount}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="budget-row">
                    <span>Utilization:</span>
                    <span class="amount overspend">{{utilizationPercentage}}%</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if recentTransactions}}
            <div class="recent-transactions">
                <h3>Recent {{categoryName}} Transactions</h3>
                {{#each recentTransactions}}
                <div class="transaction-item">
                    <div class="transaction-description">
                        <div>{{this.description}}</div>
                        <div class="transaction-date">{{this.date}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="transaction-amount">{{../currency}}{{this.amount}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="tips">
                <h3>ðŸ’¡ Suggestions for {{categoryName}} Spending</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Review recent {{categoryName}} transactions to identify patterns</li>
                    <li>Consider setting a lower budget for this category next period</li>
                    <li>Look for alternative options that cost less in this category</li>
                    <li>Set up alerts at 80% to prevent future overspending</li>
                    {{#if subcategories}}
                    <li>Consider breaking down {{categoryName}} into subcategories for better tracking</li>
                    {{/if}}
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="actions">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/budgets/{{budgetId}}?category={{categoryId}}" class="button">Review Category</a>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/transactions?category={{categoryId}}" class="button">View Transactions</a>
            </div>

            <p>This alert was triggered when your {{categoryName}} spending exceeded its allocated budget. You can adjust category budgets and alert settings in your budget management page.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/settings/notifications">Manage Notifications</a> | 
                <a href="{{supportUrl}}">Contact Support</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
